\begin_layout Standard
This practice led research project studies the practical and applied visualisati
on and exploration of texts.
 Practical because the main outputs —the artifacts— of the research, will
 be a number of developed tools published under free licenses; applied because
 the goal of this project is to demonstrate the utility of the tools developed
 to visualise and explore real world texts.
\end_layout

